sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Participant
    participant API as DALP API
    participant COMP as Compliance Engine
    participant AML as AML / Sanctions
    participant AUDIT as Audit Log
    participant OPS as Ops Team

    P->>API: Submit transaction
    API->>COMP: Pre-trade compliance check
    COMP->>AML: Sanction screening (OFAC, UN, CBE)
    AML-->>COMP: Screen result
    alt Clean
        COMP-->>API: Approved
        API-->>P: Transaction proceeds
        COMP->>AUDIT: Log approval + evidence
    else Alert
        COMP->>OPS: Alert raised
        COMP->>AUDIT: Log hold + reason code
        OPS-->>COMP: Investigation outcome
        COMP-->>API: Release or block
    end
